        <div class="mg-reflex-nickname">THE SAFETY VALVE</div>
        <div class="mg-reflex-row"><span class="mg-reflex-icon">📍</span><div class="mg-reflex-text"><b>Location:</b> Muscle-tendon junction</div></div>
        <div class="mg-reflex-row"><span class="mg-reflex-icon">👁️</span><div class="mg-reflex-text"><b>Detects:</b> Excessive tension / force</div></div>
